Pantheon Music Engine v0.1

Convert meaning → music.

What it does

Takes any prompt (story, idea, feeling) and turns it into a structured music generation spec.

Core idea

Meaning first. Style second.

Usage

Run:

python app.py --style "cinematic rock" "A silent guardian carries a kingdom through collapse."

Output
	•	Title
	•	Style
	•	Emotion profile
	•	Structure
	•	Sonic palette
	•	Hook
	•	Optional lyric seed

Principle

Small input → large structured output.
